<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把特勒尔拉到一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人偷走了展会上的玩偶。” 她小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你好运！” 特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会跟杰克和玛拉说你得回家一趟。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了美罗城会展中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在跟一些人说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他手里举着一件很小的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“侦探先生，这件衣服对您来说太小了吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱着眉头说：“哈哈，火箭女孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这件衣服是玩偶的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是一个非常特别的玩偶。” 一个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着绿色的西服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个玩偶花了我很多钱，它来自欧洲。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的玩偶都是上百年的，” 一个女人擦着眼泪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在都不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的玩偶也不见了！” 另外一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探拿出笔记本。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人看到小偷了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿绿色西服的男人吸了吸鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，当时我们在另外一个房间里吃午饭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到一声巨响，好像是玻璃被打碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们跑进来后......” 她开始哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人拍了拍她的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贝蒂，没事儿的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿会帮我们找到玩偶的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着罗西说，“对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我尽力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西没想到这些人会这么喜欢他们的玩偶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也听到小偷的声音了。” 另外一个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当时，我正在出口附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我听到有人说‘我很坏，很坏，很坏！’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我大概知道谁是小偷了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在我侄子的生日派对上，有一个叫查克的表演者，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他有一个很大的玩偶，表演得很差劲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说了同样的话，‘我很坏，很坏，很坏！’。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果查克表演得很差劲的话，” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说不定他会去做小偷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有他的名片，”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探从口袋里掏出名片一看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就住在附近，我们去看看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和史密斯侦探来到查克的家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门开着，他们走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“查克在吗？” 史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们听到呜呜的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西冲到衣柜前，打开一看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面有一个被绑着的男人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探赶紧解开了他的绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！” 查克说，“你们来得太好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它太坏了，完全失控了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦？” 罗西挠了挠头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们以为是你偷走了玩偶，才来这里的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>查克摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是我做的，是它做的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？” 史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还能是谁？” 查克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的玩偶查克斯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>